<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/ArchitecturalStructure-runwayName>
        rdf:type  sh:PropertyShape ;
        sh:class  <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/ArchitecturalStructure> ;
        sh:path   rel:runwayName .

<http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Organisation-aircraftHelicopter>
